      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STEELY DAWN (4) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when fifth (24.07) in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Normally safely away but always well back and facing a task from wide out last time. Solid record here at this trip including seven wins. The form out of her last race has been franked. Can bounce back. SWEETEST SMILE (7) has a strong record this track and trip with two wins and two placings from five starts. Missed the frame latest (26.78) when seventh over 457m at Q Lakeside in a Mix 5. Can feature with the right run. HOOTIN' ANGEL (1) turned in a plain performance last time when sixth at this track over 411m behind Kooringa Trish (24.08) in a Grade 4/5. Comes through a solid form race last start. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. MISS BLUE BLAZE (8) was strongly fancied last time but finished second (17.17), beaten 2.25 lengths. Likely to be in the finish again.",
